  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large cast-iron skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the sliced carrots and parsnips and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the nimono broth and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the linguine pasta and cook until it is al dente.",
    "Season the dish with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the dish hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
